The editor autocomplete updates the dropdown "arrowing" behaviour to jump over a header row, but reimplements the up/down/enter key listeners to work with the keyboard focus in the RTE instead of an input in the "outer" document.

The listeners in AUI dropdown should be made more generic so that they can be reused in the autocomplete, and the header-handling code from autocomplete should be merged into the AUI trunk.

